23 8. Requiring all entities permitted, licensed, or regulated by
24 the Board to maintain a copy of the current maximum rate schedule or
Req. No. 14028 Page 10

1 fee schedule established by the Board posted in a conspicuous place
2 and readily accessible to the public;
3 9. Requiring all entities permitted, licensed, or regulated by
4 the Board to allow the owner or agent of the owner of a motor
