12 SECTION 3. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
13 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 1003 of Title 40, unless there
14 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
15 There is hereby created in the State Treasury a revolving fund
16 for the Department of Labor, to be designated the “Oklahoma Wrecker
17 and Towing Services Revolving Fund”. The fund shall be a continuing
18 fund not subject to fiscal year limitations. All monies accruing to
19 the credit of the fund are hereby appropriated and shall be budgeted
20 and expended by the Department of Labor for the purpose of
21 administering the Oklahoma Wrecker Services Division. Expenditures
22 from the fund shall be made upon warrants issued by the State
23 Treasurer against claims filed as prescribed by law with the
24
Req. No. 14028 Page 12

1 Dire ctor of the Office of Management and Enterprise Services for
2 approval and payment.
